    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and a responsive transmission, making it ready for daily driving. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and reliability without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
